<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Account Activation | {{appName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #2196F3; }
    .content { padding: 30px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #2196F3; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1 style="color: #2196F3; margin: 0;">Activate Your Account</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
      <p>Your account has been successfully created! To start using {{appName}}, please activate your account by clicking the button below:</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{activationLink}}" class="button">Activate Account</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>This activation link will expire in 48 hours. If you don't activate within this time, you'll need to request a new activation email.</p>
      
      <p><strong>What happens after activation?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Full access to all {{appName}} features</li>
        <li>Ability to customize your profile</li>
        <li>Access to premium features</li>
        <li>Priority customer support</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
